                  leczelterin, <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__walter_QGW_II_I_1702">den geistlichen brudern <roleName type="title">bruder</roleName> Walthern, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-augustiner_eremiten">prior</roleName> dacz den
